metadata.name: Proposal Bunny
metadata.description:
"Proposal Bunny" 2020 is a Sculpture from the "Bright Future" series by the starting contemporary artist Adrian Noir. It's made from the material polished bronze. And it's created as a limited edition.

This sculpture will be represented in the Galleries of London in 2023.

The Bunny sculpture is a modern symbol of love created by Adrian Noir.
